snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
Daldal Official Trailer 
The series features Bhumi Satish Pednekkar along with Samara Tijori and Aditya Rawal in the lead roles.
Directed by Amrit Raj Gupta, Daldal is produced by Vikram Malhotra and Suresh Triveni under the banner of Abundantia Entertainment. Created for a series by Triveni, Daldal is written by Priya Saggi, Sreekanth Agneeaswaran, and Rohan Dâ€™Souza.

Â©ï¸ Saregama India Limited
Original Music Composer: Shankarâ€“Jaikishan
Original Lyricist: Hasrat Jaipuri

Official Release Date - January 30, 2026 on Prime Video India

About:
Haunted by the guilt of her past, Mumbai's newly-appointed DCP Rita Ferreira must embark on an investigation that puts her on a collision course with a cold-blooded killer, even as she has to save her life from falling apart.

Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. Additionally, Prime Videoâ€™s video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures â€“ Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Customers can also go behind the scenes of their favorite movies and series with exclusive X-Ray access. Prime Video is one benefit among many that provides savings, convenience, and entertainment as part of the Prime membership. For more info visit www.amazon.com/primevideo.

snippet.title: O Romeo Trailer Controversy | Mayasabha Is The Underdog | Dhurandhar 2 Shocking Rumours
snippet.description:
I have been very keen to cover all the developments that have happened in recent days. This includes the #oromeo trailer. The much awaited #mayasabha finally coming to theatres and the updates on #dhurandhar 2. Why are people already hating on the #shahidkapoor and #triptidimri starrer. Will #rahianilbarve prove himself after #tumbbad . Will #akshayekhanna and #vickykaushal make an appearance in Dhurandhar 2 with #ranveersingh . There are so many questions. I hope you like the video on:-

O Romeo Trailer Review & Analysis | Animal Controversy Tripti Dimri | Mayasabha Trailer Review | Tumbbad Director Returns | Dhurandhar 2 Rumours | Akshaye Khanna Returns? | Vicky Kaushal Cameo?

snippet.title: Bebe Main Badmash Banuga (Trailer) Jagjeet Sandhu - Aveera - Releasing 06-Feb-26
snippet.description:
Friday Russh Motion Pictures proudly presents the upcoming Punjabi film "Bebe Main Badmash Banuga"
Starring the immensely talented Jagjeet Sandhu and introducing a promising new face Aveera Singh Masoon. Today, we officially launch the Trailer of the film, giving you a glimpse into a gripping journey

Releasing Worldwide in Cinemas 6th February 2026, Watch the Trailer, share your thoughts in the comments, and stay connected for more updates.

Movie Credits
Movie Name: Bebe Main Badmash Banuga
Releasing Date: 06 February 2026
Starring: Jagjeet Sandhu, Aveera Singh Masson, Ashish Duggal, Sanju Solanki, Paramveer Singh, Satwant Kaur, Rahul Jungral, Ikatar Singh, Jass Longowalia, Guri Toor, Beant Singh, Brijesh Sharma
Story & Directed By: Sukhminder Dhanjal
Produced By: Rrupaali Gupta, Jagjeet Sandhu
Screenplay: Nihal Purba & Gurpreet Bhullar
Dialogues: Gurpreet Bhullar
Executive Producer: Jeet Bhangu
Line Producer: Gavy Mano Chahal
DOP: Hapreet
Film Editor: Gurjeet King
Action Director: Mukesh Kamboj
Music: Crowny
Lyrics: Kang Sadiq
Background Score: Kevin Roy
Art Director: Reetika Tanwar
Costume Designer: Monika Heer & Bir Kaur
Associate Director: Vishavjeet Singh
Post Production Supervision: Gurpreet Singh Bachhal
Visual promotions: Trailer Bazaar (Nikhil Soni)
Digital Promotions: GK Digital
Production: Immpossible Film Studios
Interactive/Digital: Gurpiar Singh
Soundtrack Distributions: GK Digital

A lo-fi bhajan combines traditional devotional music with the soothing, nostalgic qualities of lo-fi music. It features serene melodies and gentle rhythms that evoke a sense of peace and spiritual contemplation. The instrumentation often includes acoustic instruments like tabla, harmonium, sitar, and flute, layered over subtle lo-fi elements such as vinyl crackles or ambient sounds. The vocals, whether solo or in chorus, deliver devotional lyrics with heartfelt emotion, encouraging a meditative and reflective mood. This fusion creates a unique listening experience that merges ancient spiritual traditions with contemporary lo-fi aesthetics, offering a tranquil journey into inner harmony and reverence.

#GopalBhar #à¦—à§‹à¦ªà¦¾à¦²à¦­à¦¾à¦à¦¡à¦¼ #SonyAath #BestOfGopalBhar #BanglaStories #BengaliFolkTales #à¦—à§‹à¦ªà¦¾à¦²à¦­à¦¾à¦à¦¡à¦¼à¦à¦°à¦—à¦²à§à¦ª  #BengaliComedy #MoralStoriesBangla #FunnyFolkTales #StorytimeWithGopal #IndianFolkTales #WittyGopal #à¦—à¦²à§à¦ªà§‡à¦°à¦à§à¦²à¦¿ #FolkHeroGopal

About the show
-----------------------------
Gopal Bhar was a legendary court jester in medieval Bengal. He was in the court of Raja Krishnachandra, the famous king of Nadia in the 18th century AD. Such was the genius of Gopal that the King considered him a Navaratna of his court. His statue can still be seen in the palace of Raja Krishnachandra. Stories about his exploits are narrated in Bengal to this day and are immortalized in countless short stories. The stories are short, beautiful, humorous, and have a specific social message. Gopal Bhar is famous for stories of his wisdom, in which he outwits other fellow courtiers.
